## Regression check against Phase 5

- Re-run Phase 5's GET /api/orders for Alice after cancelling — the
  order's `status` field must now read CANCELLED everywhere it's returned
  (single-order GET and the list GET), with no other field changed.
- Re-run Phase 3/4's GET /api/products/10000000-...-0001 and ...-0003 —
  stockCount must be back to its pre-order value (25 and 40) after the
  cancellation's ReleaseStock call, exactly as proved non-interactively in
  Database-Dev step 11.
